<style>
.testimonials{background:#fff;padding:80px 20px}
.testimonials h2{text-align:center;font-size:2rem;color:#1f2937;margin:0 0 50px}
.testimonial-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:30px;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto}
.testimonial{background:#f9fafb;padding:35px;border-radius:12px;border-left:4px solid #3b82f6;transition:transform .3s}
.testimonial:hover{transform:translateY(-5px)}
.testimonial .quote{font-size:1.05rem;color:#374151;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;font-style:italic}
.testimonial .author{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:15px}
.testimonial .author-info strong{display:block;color:#1f2937;font-size:1rem}
.testimonial .author-info span{color:#6b7280;font-size:.9rem}
.testimonial .stars{color:#fbbf24;font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:15px}
</style>

<section class="testimonials">
  <h2>What Our Clients Say</h2>
  <div class="testimonial-grid">
    <div class="testimonial">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="quote">"JCS saved us over ₹80,000 last year by catching TDS errors we didn't even know about. Their monthly reports help us make better inventory decisions. Best decision we made for our business."</p>
      <div class="author">
        <div class="author-info">
          <strong>Rajesh Kumar</strong>
          <span>Manufacturing Unit, Mayapuri</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="quote">"Before JCS, we got hit with ₹45,000 in late PF penalties. Now everything is filed on time, every month. Their payroll service is worth every rupee—we get payslips by WhatsApp in 2 hours."</p>
      <div class="author">
        <div class="author-info">
          <strong>Priya Sharma</strong>
          <span>Coaching Institute, Janakpuri</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="quote">"We had a labour court case that could have cost us ₹12 lakhs. JCS connected us with an excellent advocate and the case settled for ₹3 lakhs. Their legal network is solid."</p>
      <div class="author">
        <div class="author-info">
          <strong>Amit Verma</strong>
          <span>Restaurant Chain, Rohini</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="quote">"Tried doing GST ourselves for 6 months—nightmare. JCS took over and within 3 months we had audit-ready books. Their WhatsApp support is incredibly responsive."</p>
      <div class="author">
        <div class="author-info">
          <strong>Neha Gupta</strong>
          <span>E-commerce Startup, Gurgaon</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="quote">"Their hospitality staffing saved our office opening. We needed 8 housekeeping staff in 48 hours—JCS delivered trained, verified staff on time. Professional service."</p>
      <div class="author">
        <div class="author-info">
          <strong>Sandeep Singh</strong>
          <span>Corporate Office, Noida</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
